[Name] XMobar
[Summary] Xmobar is a minimalistic text based status bar.
[Description] Inspired by the Ion3 status bar, it supports similar features, like \
dynamic color management, output templates, and extensibility through plugins.
[License] BSD License (revised) (3-clause)
[Homepage] http://hackage.haskell.org/cgi-bin/hackage-scripts/package/xmobar
